text:
Team SFN is considering two solutions for their driver restraining system:
Solution A is from a well-known manufacturer based in Europe. Their 2020 system includes an antisubmarine strap, two shoulder straps and two lap belts, all belts have a width of 75mm. The system will be bought new from the manufacturer in 2020 and it meets the FIA specification 8853/2016.
Solution B is a second hand system in mint condition, previously used by a rallycross team. This 6- point system has belts with a minimum width of 75mm and it meets SFI Specification 16.5. The manufacturing date on the label reads 01/01/2020.
Which solution(s) is/are compliant with the rules and eglible to use at FSN2020?

Your team set the fastest lap time at the Autocross event with a time of 86,3 seconds on your first and only run. However, on the final scoring sheet your team is listed in fifth place with 73,1 out of 100 points, while the new winner of the event has a corrected elapsed time of 87,1 seconds.
How many cones did your team knock Down or Out?

Two team members are presenting the Business Plan Presentation. After the introduction, team member A forgets all of his text. Luckily, team member B can finish the presentation by herself. After the presentation is completed, the FSN judges have a few questions for the team members. Which statement is correct?

answer_options.answer_text: Both team members may answer questions from the judges
Only team member A may answer questions from the judges
Only team member B may answer questions from the judges
None of the team members may answer questions from the judges

answers.answer_text: Both team members may answer questions from the judges
Only team member A may answer questions from the judges
Only team member B may answer questions from the judges
None of the team members may answer questions from the judges

Your team has brought three sets of rims, tow sets of dry tires and one set wet tires to FSN2019.
At technical inspection, you present the rim/tyre type combinations: A-1, B-2 and C-3. All are approved by the scrutieers. Befor the endruance event you decide to change your set due to a broken rim in set B. Which new combination are you allowed to use?
These details are known:

answer_options.answer_text: You are not allowed to change

answers.answer_text: You are not allowed to change
